def main():
    juice = input().split()
    recipe = input().split()
    for i in range(3):
        juice[i] = float(juice[i])
        recipe[i] = float(recipe[i])
    juice = sorted(juice)
    recipe = sorted(recipe)
    while(juice[0] > 0 and recipe[0] > 0):
        for i in range(3):
            juice[i] -= recipe[i]
        juice = sorted(juice)
        recipe = sorted(recipe)
    for i in range(3):
        print("{0:.6f}".format(juice[i]))

main()

import sys

def cocktail(juice, ratio):
    """Calculates the leftovers from a cocktail"""
    juice_leftover = []
    min_juice = min(juice)
    min_ratio = min(ratio)
    min_cocktail = min_juice / min_ratio
    for i in range(len(juice)):
        juice_leftover.append(juice[i] - (min_cocktail * ratio[i]))
    return juice_leftover

def main():
    """Main function"""
    data = sys.stdin.read().splitlines()
    juice = list(map(int, data[0].split()))
    ratio = list(map(int, data[1].split()))
    juice_leftover = cocktail(juice, ratio)
    for leftover in juice_leftover:
        print("{0:.6f}".format(leftover))

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
